quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  25,61,"Ubutagatifu ni ubw’uwashyize inyenyeri nini mu kirere, akanashyiramo itara ryaka (izuba) ndetse n’ukwezi kumurika"
  25,62,Ni na We washyizeho ugusimburana kw’ijoro n’amanywa (kugira ngo bibere isomo) wa wundi ushaka kwibuka cyangwa gushimira
  25,63,Kandi abagaragu ba (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe ni ba bandi bagenda ku isi biyoroheje. N’iyo injiji zibavugishije (amagambo mabi) baravuga bati “Amahoro!”
  25,64,"Ni na bo barara amajoro bubama, ndetse banahagaze (basingiza) Nyagasani wabo"
  25,65,"Ni na bo bavuga bati “Nyagasani wacu! Dukize ibihano by’umuriro wa Jahanamu, kubera ko mu by’ukuri ibihano byawo bizahoraho.”"
  25,66,Mu by’ukuri (umuriro) ni ho hantu habi ho kuba no gutura
  25,67,"Ni na bo batanga (mu byo batunze) badasesagura, cyangwa ngo bagundire. Ahubwo bajya hagati y’ibyo byombi"
  25,68,"Ni na bo batabangikanya Allah n’izindi mana, ntibice icyo Allah yaziririje bitanyuze mu kuri, kandi ntibanasambane. Kandi ukora ibyo azahura n’ibihano (bibabaza)"
  25,69,"Azongererwa ibihano ku munsi w’imperuka, kandi azabibamo ubuziraherezo asuzuguritse"
  25,70,"Usibye uzicuza akanemera (Allah) ndetse akanakora ibikorwa byiza; abo ibikorwa byabo bibi Allah azabihinduramo ibyiza. Kandi Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimpuhwe"
  25,71,"Kandi uwicujije akanakora ibyiza, mu by’ukuri aba yicujije kuri Allah ukwicuza nyako"
  25,72,"(Abagaragu ba Nyirimpuhwe kandi) ni na bo batajya baba abahamya b’ibinyoma, kandi iyo banyuze ku bidafite akamaro, babinyuraho biyubashye"
  25,73,"Ni na bo kandi igihe bibukijwe amagambo ya Nyagasani wabo, batifata nk’abatumva cyangwa nk’abatabona"
  25,74,"Ni na bo kandi bavuga bati “Nyagasani wacu! Duhe kunezezwa n’abagore bacu ndetse n’urubyaro rwacu, kandi utugire kuba abayobozi b’abagandukiramana.”"
  25,75,Abo ni bo bazahembwa imyanya yo hejuru (mu ijuru) kubera ukwihangana kwabo. Bazakirizwamo indamutso n’amagambo by’amahoro
  25,76,Bazabamo ubuziraherezo. Ni ho hantu heza ho kuba no gutura
  25,77,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Iyo bitaza kuba ugusaba kwanyu, Nyagasani wanjye ntiyari kubitaho ariko (mwebwe abahakanyi) mwahinyuye (Intumwa ye). Bityo ibihano byanyu bizahoraho.”"